.\" Synthetic reproducer: a Pandoc-style page whose only structure is .SS
.\" subsections with no enclosing .SH. libmandoc parses it, but the lowering
.\" used to drop every root-level .SS and report "no readable sections".
.TH "subsection_only" "3" "" "Version 1" "ManT fixture"
.SS Name
subsection_only \- a page built only from subsections
.SS Synopsis
.EX
int subsection_only(void);
.EE
.SS Description
Body text that lives directly under a subsection heading.
.SS Return value
Returns zero on success or a non-zero value on error.
